  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">3FM Seroius Request 2018: Lifeline in conflicts</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Every 2 seconds, someone in the world is forced to leave his/her home due to conflict or war. Ordinary civilians who are the victims of battles and oppression in their country. Some people look for safety elsewhere. The majority stays behind and tries to survive in damaged homes, often with constant threat of violence, lack of health care and with limited money for food and drinks. The Red Cross provides medical support, but also helps to provide primary needs such as safe water, food and shelter. With 3FM Serious Request: Lifeline, we get into action for these people.</narrative>
  </description>
